room_title: Escape room "The Pirate Ship" by Solve the Room Hawaii in Honolulu
room_description:
Your uncle takes you and your friends on vacation to sail the waters of Hawaii. While out sailing, you encounter an abandoned pirate ship in the distance. Your uncle tells you the mystery of pirates who sailed this ship. Legend has it, these pirates died at sea, leaving a treasure hidden somewhere on the ship.
You board the ship, eager to be the ones to find the missing treasure. You immediately start looking for clues. All of a sudden you realize there is a hole in the ship and it is quickly filling up with water. You are determined to find that treasure, but you only have one hour before the ship visits Davy Jonesâ€™s locker at the bottom of the sea forever...
